br><br><P ALIGN=Center><br><B>You ask why I do not know my people, and how I came to be so far away.  My mother fell in love w/ a man, named Dasirus.  He was travelor of the great waters, what some would call a pirate.<BR><br>He took her far from her land and people. And I...I was born of this union. Born on the sea.  I have lived my whole life journeying from land to land.  Til the day, my father's ship was taken in a battle near the lands the Rome Empire.  My father was killed in the battle...and my mother and I were taken as slaves by these pirates.  And then sold on land.   </B></P><br><BR><br><IMG SRC="http://www.themiscrya.i-p.com/17f_freeman.jpg" HEIGHT=239 WIDTH=150 ALIGN=Right><br></A><br><BR><br><P ALIGN=Left><br><B>We were sold to a roman soldier, of high rank.  And taken to a city called Rome.  It was a large city...with many people and tall white buildings.  There we were put in cages with other people.  I soon found out that we were to be used in their games.  A bloody game of death and lions.  My mother...she lost her "game".   </B></P><br><BR><br><P ALIGN=Center><br><B>Then the day came...and it was my turn.  But, for some reason...my game was different.  I was to fight a woman.  Her name was Livia.  She seemed to be one of their great warriors.  I was given a shield and a sword.  I prayed to the great spirit, Yhi...whom my mother had told me was for our people.  And somehow...I beat this great warrior.  And...in this..I earned respect.   I was taken in with the warriors of these people and trained. I was be a slave warrior.  After several months... I was allowed to walk the streets.  They had begun to trust me. Fools.  In the dark of the night...I ran.  I ran as hard and fast as my legs could possibly take me.</B></P><br><BR><br><P ALIGN=Center><br><B>Until, one night  I came upon a tavern filled with warrior women.  That night changed my life.  Since then, I have made many friends among the amazons.  And especially, I have come to respect and enjoy the friendship of Alysia and Hippolyte, both Queens.  I have a home both in Scynthia and Themiscrya.  Yhi has blessed me well.</B></P><br><br> <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uarahutajiwarli.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Arahuta Jiwarli</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.hometown.aol.com/arahutajiwarli/star-14.gif" BORDER=0> at: 1/25/02 5:24:23 pm<br></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm33.showPrevMessage?topicID=42.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm33.showNextMessage?topicID=42.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm33.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=42.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/addReply1.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm33.emailToFriend?topicID=42.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm33.threadControl?topicID=42.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/deleteThreadFire.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm33.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=42.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm33.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=42.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub11.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><tabl